code: @Override public StreamPartitioner<Tuple> createPartitioner() {     StreamPartitioner<Tuple> partitioner = new ShufflePartitioner<>().     assertFalse(partitioner.isBroadcast()).     return partitioner. }

@Test public void testSelectChannelsInterval() {     assertSelectedChannelWithSetup(0, 1).     streamPartitioner.setup(2).     assertTrue(0 <= streamPartitioner.selectChannel(serializationDelegate)).     assertTrue(2 > streamPartitioner.selectChannel(serializationDelegate)).     streamPartitioner.setup(1024).     assertTrue(0 <= streamPartitioner.selectChannel(serializationDelegate)).     assertTrue(1024 > streamPartitioner.selectChannel(serializationDelegate)). }
